opendial.state.distribs

Class OutputDistribution

  • java.lang.Object
    • opendial.state.distribs.OutputDistribution
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ProbDistribution

    public class OutputDistribution
extends java.lang.Object
implements ProbDistribution
    Representation of an output distribution (see Pierre Lison's PhD thesis, page 70 for details), which is a reflection of the combination of effects specified in the parent rules.
    Author:
    Pierre Lison (plison@ifi.uio.no)
